            "is_major": false,
            "source": "GlobeNewswire",
            "source_type": "news",
            "summary": "In Vancouver, British Columbia, as of February 20, 2025, Imperial Metals Corporation disclosed that the 2024 metal production from Red Chris reached 85,320,618 pounds of copper and 59,811 ounces of gold on a 100% basis. This marked an increase from the 2023 production of 57,051,467 pounds of copper and 46,046 ounces of gold. The elevated production was attributed to higher grades and recoveries for both metals. Red Chris successfully achieved its 2024 production target of 85.0 million pounds of copper and 57,000 ounces of gold for the calendar year 2024.",
